<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.10.9">
<l>vaṅka malipauva matumāmu kaṭiṉucci pukamikka perunīr</l>
<l>aṅka maḻiyāra vaṉatāṇai talaicūṭu maṭiyāra ṟitiyēl</l>
<l>poṅku puṉaluntu maṇikaṅku liruḷcīṟu moḷiyeṅku muḷatāl</l>
<l>naṅkaḷ perumāṉu ṟaiyumnanti puraviṇṇa karamnaṇṇu maṉamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The bodies of devotees who crown their heads with his bed</l>
<l rend="indent">will not perish in the great waters,</l>
<l>When the sea, where waves swell, reaches the top of the great, high peaks;</l>
<l>If you know [that], O heart, go to Nantipura Viṇṇakaram</l>
<l rend="indent">where dwells our great lord,</l>
<l>Where the brilliance of jewels which dispels the darkness of night,</l>
<l rend="indent">having been cast up by crashing waves, is truly everywhere.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
